<div id="Idea_4264"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/4264-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_4264">Mr. President-Make completely available long form birth certificate and all school records&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/10567-4049">marquis4homes</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">6 hours ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Hello Mr. Barack Obama. I do not see why you would not want to clear up once and for all, the nagging question that hundreds of thousands of Americans have. Where is your Long form Birth Certificate? I feel that you have an obligation, a duty, and commitment to all Americans, to represent who you are, where you came from, and your eligibility to be President of the United States. It is very, very easy to do this. The Certification of Live Birth that you have been hiding behind on your website is not a Birth Certificate. I have a birth certificate which includes the hospital, date/time of birth, the doctor that delivered me, a witness, both my father and mother and their occupation, my weight, size and the Great Seal of California. Yours does not have any of this which really makes me suspect that you received a Certification of Live Birth given to those born out of country but is registered as a birth within Hawaii statutes as outlined in there by-laws. You need to clear up two things. Completely release all records pertaining to your original birth certificate, and completely release all records of your high school and college records, especially your enrollment and eligible status to receive government grants, funding, or loans from the United States Government or State Government. You say you want to be transparent. Well now you can. If you do not do this, many Americans will always think you are a fraud, hiding behind a copy print of a Hawaiian Certification of Live Birth. I will be the first one to apologize to you, if you can prove who you are. </div>
