<td valign="top" style="padding-right:30px; padding-left:20px;">
<div id="Idea_4195"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/4195-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_4195">Reduce Contract waste and duplication by making things transparent&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/10075-4049">jill.m.powell</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">18 hours ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">I am a contractor so, I am probably shooting myself in the foot for saying this but as a tax payer and a concern citizen and one who cares deeply about each and every soldier we need to stop wasting money on projects that contractors perform that are duplication. We have no visibility of what products and services that are created that could be leveraged if there was transparency and visibility. If we could create a central repository of all contracts products and services that could be categorized and searched we could leverage all products and services. Often due to lack of transparency and visibility we reinvent the wheel and do not reuse products and services already in place. I work for the Army Knowledge Management Office (BCKS)on Ft. Leavenworth and I believe we could help greatly in this effort.</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_4195" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_4195', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2236&topicID=4195')">Comments (0)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_4195"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2236">Making Data More Accessible</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=waste">waste</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=transparency">transparency</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=contracts">contracts</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=reinventing the wheel">reinventing the wheel</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=share knowledge">share knowledge</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_4195"></div>
</div></td>
</tr>
</table>

